<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道，我们数的人参果数量是对的。”一个道士说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不管怎样，我们会去再数一遍的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个非常生气的道士出去了，结果吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人参果树倒在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整棵树都变成了灰色，所有叶子都掉光了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人参果树死了！”一个道士大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定是那个猴子干的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但那猴子一直在房间里。”另一个道士说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他怎么能同一时间来这里毁了树呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个神仙。”第一个道士说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一定是施了法术。”他看着那棵树摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这树比天地都要老。那猴子一定很厉害。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们和他打的话会很危险。”另一个道士说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们等镇元大仙回来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道观里，唐僧正在责备他的徒弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是客人。”他说，“</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很生气，你们居然偷主人的果子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士们回来了。“我们得向你们道歉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个道士说，“人参果一个都没少。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。”唐僧说，“听到这个消息真是太好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你的道歉。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空怀疑地看了看两个道士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道他们在说谎，但他不知道他们为什么说谎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们欢迎你们在这里过夜。”一个道士说，“跟我们来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士领着唐僧一行人进了道观里的一个小房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧和他的徒弟们都走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这房间不错。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空注意到那两个道士并没有进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正要说些什么，一个道士突然关上了门，把门锁上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！”八戒大叫，“你们这是什么主人！你把我们锁起来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘣！他用力地在门上踹了一脚。“哦！我的脚！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒倒在了地上，不停地揉着脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们为什么要把我们锁在这里？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们怕我们。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把他们的人参果树弄倒了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”唐僧大叫。“我很生气。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们可能是计划把我们锁在这里直到他们的师父回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧瞪着他的徒弟们。“和你们这样的徒弟一起，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要怎么去西方极乐世界？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒站起来：“这不是我的错。我那会儿饿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净低着头。“师父，别担心。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会把大家弄出去的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等那道士睡了，我就用我的解锁术，然后我们就继续上路。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，他们四个人溜了出去，继续朝西走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，他们在路上遇到了一个老人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打扰一下。”老人说，“你们是从道观那里来的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧紧张地看着他的徒弟。“嗯，是的。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想也是。”老人说。他突然变高了很多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是镇元大仙！你们毁了我的人参果树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除非你们给我一棵新的，否则你们别想走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了他的金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净举起了兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇元大仙升到了空中，站在一朵云上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑：“你觉得你能飞就很厉害吗？我们都会飞！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇元大仙抬起了一边的眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会这个吗？这叫袖里乾坤。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇元大仙挥动着手臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的袖子向悟空和他的同伴们扫过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们立刻就被扫进了那袖子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>